We didn't even know that.

00:12:04.420 --> 00:12:06.410
But this configuration file,
it sets it up,

00:12:06.530 --> 00:12:10.390
and it just automatically restarts,
and then you're set to go.

00:12:10.770 --> 00:12:11.900
All right, thanks, Eric.

