00:12:26.880 --> 00:12:29.840
So another area that we've
improved in Panther Server is

00:12:29.840 --> 00:12:31.420
the administration tools.

00:12:31.420 --> 00:12:33.530
We've taken all of the
administration tools and

00:12:33.530 --> 00:12:36.980
integrated them into a single app,
which allows you to set up and monitor

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:40.340
your services on a day-to-day basis.

