I'm going to go to my Apple File Server,

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:11.560
and I'm going to make some
changes to the configuration.

00:14:11.600 --> 00:14:16.110
So I'm going to say,
welcome to my server.

00:14:16.900 --> 00:14:18.230
Server Rocks.

00:14:18.230 --> 00:14:22.260
And I can go in here and change,
you know, configuration methods.

00:14:22.260 --> 00:14:23.470
You know, that's great.

00:14:23.480 --> 00:14:24.160
Any method.

00:14:24.160 --> 00:14:28.180
I can set it to only, you know,
