00:20:33.860 --> 00:20:37.220
So we've done a lot of work in the user
interface here to really improve this,

00:20:37.230 --> 00:20:38.260
make it easy to understand.

00:20:38.260 --> 00:20:41.600
You can also go through and
configure the different protocols,

00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:43.580
search bases, set up SSL authentication.

