00:20:50.690 --> 00:20:53.650
be at least a certain number of
characters long or differ from the

00:20:53.700 --> 00:20:57.560
last four passwords that you've used,
I can make that change and impose that

00:20:57.560 --> 00:20:59.340
upon all the users in the network.

