We're changing the build style of PHP,
so we're actually including more

00:40:25.340 --> 00:40:30.440
of the development functions that
people needed in our PHP module.

00:40:30.440 --> 00:40:31.920
So that'll be good for development.

00:40:31.940 --> 00:40:33.470
developers.

00:40:34.260 --> 00:40:39.570
So basically taking all of
these things-- I don't know if

00:40:39.570 --> 00:40:39.570
you guys can read all of that.

00:40:40.570 --> 00:40:44.060
Mac OS X Server basically has everything
needed to create three-tier websites

00:40:44.150 --> 00:40:45.920
or entire websites on Mac OS X Server.

00:40:45.920 --> 00:40:49.080
We include a bunch of
stuff to do your own thing.

00:40:49.080 --> 00:40:53.580
If you've got third-party products,
you can grab as well 4D, Oracle.

00:40:53.580 --> 00:40:58.030
So it's a great development
platform for web development.

